  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为Kikwiflow平台画一张架构图，核心要体现它是嵌入式运行的，并且支持CQRS模式。我想把整体分成三大块：用户应用层、Kikwiflow平台层，还有数据层。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Sua Aplicação (Spring Boot)",
        "Plataforma Kikwiflow (Embarcada)",
        "Camada de Dados (Pluggable)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，三层结构。用户应用层用Spring Boot，平台层标注为嵌入式，数据层做成可插拔的。颜色上我打算用紫色系给用户层，蓝色给平台层，绿色给数据层，这样区分度够吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UserApp",
        "KikwiflowPlatform",
        "DataLayer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，但用户应用层的填充色用浅紫#f3e8ff，边框用#a855f7，平台层用#e0f2fe配#0ea5e9，数据层用#dcfce7配#22c55e。这样更贴合我们的品牌规范。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UserApp",
        "KikwiflowPlatform",
        "DataLayer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，三个子图的颜色和边框宽度都设置好了。现在细化用户应用层内部，需要放哪些组件？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UserApp"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "用户层放两个东西：一是用户自己的业务代码，比如Controller和Service；二是一个可选的管理API，叫KikwiRestApi。后者不是必须的，所以要标注清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UserCode",
        "KikwiRestApi"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
