      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "收到，UserCode标注为'Seu Código de Negócio'，KikwiRestApi标注为'API REST de Gerenciamento'并加斜体说明是可选的。接下来平台层内部怎么划分？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UserCode",
        "KikwiRestApi"
