      "utterance": "平台层是重点，要体现CQRS。我需要一个子图叫'Orquestração e Consulta (CQRS)'，里面放CommandEngine和QueryService。CommandEngine就是KikwiflowEngine，QueryService对应ExternalTaskQueryService。",
